2cd21510f2a27a5cbfd4780ccda5a10f2190b911","tid":1287461,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T15:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cda118ca8a474f3b44603a7f866e4fd9e9bdc49","tid":1287461,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T00:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e713e3e741a0fd56bbd19ffce710ae86f5c5c8e","tid":1287461,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T01:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1a49e9e791b1f8b3907fc0171b98fe1a0ca97f","tid":1287461,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T03:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b9e505a0d255cb3ee33d5c909e490328b34a52","tid":1287461,"uid":193475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa9c87d0c88d870aa37b55ec48bfb362ec8f1449","tid":1287461,"uid":72795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:22:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: right;\">2051年9月9日 香城</div><br />\n學生會發言人回應今日獲邀請出席閉門會議時表示，我們留意到今次的會議以閉門方式進行， 學生會一向尊重學生集會和表達意見的自由和權利，亦明白學生對學生會的政策有不同意見。理性包容、和而不同是香港這個自由和多元化社會的特質，也是香港人引以為傲的核心價值。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示：「學生會清楚明白不少學生對修訂《逃犯條例》的擔心和疑慮，並已停止所有關於出席閉門會議的工作，出席草案會在現屆學生會會期於今年七月結束時自動失效。」<br />\n<br />\n發言人重申，學生會從沒為閉門會議「定性」；而無論任何人就任何事件如何「定性」，均不影響學生會的會議出席工作。<br />\n<br />\n發言人指根據學生會主席陳大文已「向學生會成員建議會方應主動審視近期的大型公眾活動，以履行其法定職能。現時，會方正就有關建議進行內部討論，其網頁亦正進行改版以配合相關工作。學生會將於短期內就其未來計劃向學生作出交代。」<br />\n<br />\n今日部分政府人士從早到晚與學生對峙，衝擊學生防線，破壞社會秩序，嚴重影響學生安全，部分激進公務員不斷以極端暴力衝擊學生會，嚴重影響學生和公眾安全。這些暴力行為，絕對不為社會接受，學生會予以強烈譴責，使用暴力的政府人士必須立即停止暴力行為。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:42:47.000Z","msg":"你好 我借用左你的文章做了個voice over.... 想問下巴打/ 絲打有冇興趣寫多幾篇香城文章? <br />\n<br />\n麻煩PM我 thank you! <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/WAKAKA_smile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWAKAKA_smile&d=dy0aigSTvaZIWgiFf%2BaM%2BMIAfqyfHgkV2drMeooGLQQ%3D&h=d4199bcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WAKAKA_smile</a>"},{"pid":"27596f1ba25af10ea50bb16ee8c1711843068964","tid":1287461,"uid":146390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883b697a086c1dacc7085e2d7087aeac55167410","tid":1287461,"uid":270912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:57:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}